This project will focus on building a production-ready RAG chatbot for the automotive domain, handling multiple document formats (PDFs, spreadsheets, manuals, etc.) with complex content like images, diagrams, tables, and technical specifications.

Document Types to Include
Type	Formats	Content Examples
Car Manuals	PDF, DOCX	Text, diagrams, troubleshooting tables
Spec Sheets	PDF, XLSX, CSV	Engine specs, dimensions, performance data
Service Guides	PDF, PPTX	Repair procedures, wiring diagrams
Parts Catalog	CSV, XLSX	Part numbers, prices, compatibility tables
Recall Notices	PDF, HTML	Safety recalls, defect descriptions